{"tid":1593120,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Breaking news]日本國民男友竹內涼真出柜！對象居然是韓國top男團成員？","createTime":"2019-09-25T02:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T10:06:59.000Z","uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7133117ba3e382eb051f47ef8c943471b08793e6","tid":1593120,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:33:49.000Z","msg":"事實上竹內涼真本來應該不太認識防彈的成員，不過粉絲問到後就表示他們有很多好歌，更哼出日本單曲《Lights》。而他唯獨記得其中一個有藍色頭髮的成員，於是便問旁人是誰。工作人員也立即解答是泰泰（V的別名），結果竹內涼真就開始不斷讚賞V的顏值，說他實在是太漂亮了，自己亦輸給他。接著竹內涼真更表示：「如果是泰泰我可以跟他接吻，太漂亮了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CfCQdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CfCQdQ.png&h=c5a27d97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDHYzFE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDHYzFE.gif&h=cc2b4f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05383b9656a9d81573e05e13da1d6bde07f1054","tid":1593120,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691d2a44d1938044893767e4859e14a6c848903f","tid":1593120,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https:/